name: Siup coffee
address: Jl. I.GST. NGR Rai No.16, Pangsan, Kec. Petang, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80353, Indonesia
review 1:
simple but tasty food, with great staffs and very reasonable price :) If you need short break after waterfall hiking, I highly recommend you.

Hot caffuccino with robust bean, it was so nice after I got rain!
review 2: Lovely local cafe with lovely people and good coffee. Great place to have some coffee and snack to warm up your body after waterfall.
review 3: Very simple tasty food and fresh made coffee. Coffee was delicious. Great staff. A nice place to stop on the way to Bedugal or when biking around Bongkasa. And well done interior. Enak sekali!
